01:02:13,660 --> 01:02:15,010
那該死的Miranda Tate是怎麼
What the hell did Miranda Tate

837
01:02:15,010 --> 01:02:17,450
打入Wayne集團董事會的
get the inside track on the Wayne Board?

838
01:02:17,550 --> 01:02:19,300
她難道一直和他在見面
I mean, is she been meeting with him?

839
01:02:19,300 --> 01:02:20,000
她是在和他上床嗎
Is she been sleeping with him?

840
01:02:20,000 --> 01:02:20,740
就我們所知並沒有
Not that we know of.

841
01:02:20,850 --> 01:02:23,870
得了吧 你根本也就不知道多少是吧 Bane在哪兒
Oh clearly you don't know much of anything, do you? Where's Bane?

842
01:02:23,950 --> 01:02:26,290
- 你和他說過事關緊急了嗎 - 那他人在哪兒呢
- You told him it was urgent. - Where is that man now?

843
01:02:26,370 --> 01:02:29,910
說曹操 曹操就到
Speak of the devil, and he shall appears.

844
01:02:30,000 --> 01:02:33,070
這他媽都是怎麼回事
What the hell is going on?

845
01:02:33,310 --> 01:02:36,210
一切正如計劃進行中啊
The plan is preceding as expected.

846
01:02:36,310 --> 01:02:40,350
是麼 我看上去像是已經執掌Wayne集團的樣子嘛
Really? Do I look like I'm running Wayne Enterprises right now?

847
01:02:40,460 --> 01:02:45,350
你襲擊了證券交易所 可那沒成功啊 我的朋友
Your hit on the stock exchange, it didn't work my friend.

848
01:02:45,350 --> 01:02:47,040
然後現在你又讓我的工程隊
And now you have my construction crews

849
01:02:47,040 --> 01:02:50,210
在城裡24小時到處開工
going around the city at 24 hours a day.

850
01:02:50,320 --> 01:02:55,840
這到底算哪門子的幫助我吞掉Wayne集團呢
How exactly is that suppose to help my company absorbs Wayne?

851
01:02:57,930 --> 01:03:00,490
- 退下 - 不用 你就待在這兒
- Leave us! - No! Stay here!

852
01:03:00,590 --> 01:03:02,210
我才是這兒管事的人
I'm in charge here.

853
01:03:02,870 --> 01:03:06,260
你覺得自己像麼
Do you feel in charge?

854
01:03:10,280 --> 01:03:12,060
我可是給了你不少錢
I have paid you a small fortune.

855
01:03:12,230 --> 01:03:15,470
所以你就以為自己可以壓過我了
And this gives you power over me?

856
01:03:15,760 --> 01:03:17,200
你什麼意思
What is this?

857
01:03:17,330 --> 01:03:22,700
你的錢還有工程隊起的作用真的很重要
Your money and infrastructure have been important ...

858
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:24,350
不過現在已經沒用了
... until now.

859
01:03:24,420 --> 01:03:27,500
- 你到底是什麼東西 - 我就是哥譚市的審判日
- What are you? - I'm Gotham reckoning.

860
01:03:27,610 --> 01:03:31,100
它會將你們所生活的一切終結
It'll end of all the damn you've been living on.

861
01:03:32,530 --> 01:03:35,730
你太邪惡了
You are pure evil.

862
01:03:35,750 --> 01:03:38,790
- 這是必要的嘛 - 不要
- A necessary evil. - No!

863
01:03:44,770 --> 01:03:47,330
你惹了不小的麻煩
Well you've started quite a mess.

864
01:03:47,490 --> 01:03:49,210
我只是要保護自己親近的人而已
To protect the people closes to me.

865
01:03:49,290 --> 01:03:51,160
也許你的確是個獨行俠 你沒有家庭
Maybe you're a loner, right? You didn't have a family.

866
01:03:51,270 --> 01:03:53,270
你還是有關心在乎的人啊
There are always people that you care about.

867
01:03:55,300 --> 01:03:57,860
可你就是要等到他們都不見了才意識到這點
But you didn't realize how much until they're gone.

868
01:03:57,940 --> 01:04:00,850
這只是一個象徵性的概念
The idea was to be a symbol.

869
01:04:00,950 --> 01:04:06,320
任何人都可以是蝙蝠俠 那才是重點
Batman can be anyone. That was the point.

870
01:04:06,500 --> 01:04:09,720
- 那他回來真是件大好事 - 可不是每個人都這麼想
- Well it damn good to see him back. - Not everybody agrees.

871
01:04:09,830 --> 01:04:11,520
我最終會搞明白的
I'll figured that out in the end.

872
01:04:11,530 --> 01:04:14,290
你查到Bane的行蹤了嘛
Do you got anything on Bane's whereabouts?

873
01:04:14,730 --> 01:04:18,010
是啊 我手上有500頁的地下通道地圖和一把手電筒
Yes, I have 500 pages of tunnel records and a flashlight.

874
01:04:18,100 --> 01:04:19,830
我真的很需要人幫忙
I could use some help actually.

875
01:04:21,200 --> 01:04:23,140
這樣吧 你就在老城區那裡放我下車吧
You know what, drop me in the old town.

876
01:04:27,580 --> 01:04:30,440
- 我不這麼想 - 這樣的話事情不會成功的
- I don't think so! - That is not how it works.

877
01:04:30,520 --> 01:04:32,590
他不是目標
He's not a mark.

878
01:04:32,700 --> 01:04:35,440
反正他的名號現在一分錢都不值
and he doesn't have a cent to his name anyway.

879
01:04:36,080 --> 01:04:40,220
的確是不多 不過也總比你現在要好吧
Yeah. It's not much, but it's more than you got right now.

880
01:04:40,370 --> 01:04:43,190
事實上 他們沒把我的房子收走
Actually, they're letting me keep the house.

881
01:04:43,300 --> 01:04:45,970
有錢人就算是破了產還是和我們不一樣是吧
The rich doesn't even go broke like the rest of us huh?

882
01:04:46,080 --> 01:04:50,190
我那個厲害的朋友希望你能回心轉意不要走
My powerful friend might hope to change your mind about leaving.

883
01:04:50,290 --> 01:04:52,750
- 那他準備怎麼做 - 他準備把你想要的東西給你
- And how would he do that? - By giving you what you want.

884
01:04:52,900 --> 01:04:55,970
- 那東西不存在 - 他說存在
- It doesn't exist. - He says it does.

885
01:04:56,120 --> 01:04:58,820
- 他還說想在今晚和你見面 - 為什麼
- He wants to meet tonight. - Why?

886
01:04:58,960 --> 01:05:02,990
他想找到Bane 然後說你知道怎麼找到他
He needs to find Bane. He says you know how.

887
01:05:05,730 --> 01:05:10,010
- 告訴他我會考慮的 - 好的 我挺喜歡你這地方的
- Tell him I'll think about it. - Okay. I like your place.

888
01:05:11,510 --> 01:05:13,580
Wayne先生
Mr. Wayne!

889
01:05:15,140 --> 01:05:18,030
我很抱歉他們把你的錢都奪走了
I'm sorry they took all your money.

890
01:05:18,440 --> 01:05:20,580
不 你才不抱歉
No you're not.

891
01:05:20,990 --> 01:05:23,410
- 我們有什麼能幫到你麼警官 - 有啊
- Can we help you officer? - Yeah.

892
01:05:23,520 --> 01:05:26,330
在一小時前John Daggett的屍體在一個垃圾箱裡被找到了
John Daggett's body was found in a dumpster an hour ago.

893
01:05:26,330 --> 01:05:28,800
我以為你會想知道
Thought you might wanna know.

894
01:05:28,930 --> 01:05:29,950
為什麼
Why?

895
01:05:29,960 --> 01:05:31,780
因為在哥譚市半數的隧道許可證上
Well his name is all over this permit I just

896
01:05:31,780 --> 01:05:33,440
全都有他的名字
pulled to half the tunnel under Gotham.

897
01:05:33,570 --> 01:05:37,620
都是些交通維護 下水道建設還有其他的事由
That's MTA maintenance, sewer construction and others things...

898
01:05:37,730 --> 01:05:39,960
你從這隧道裡研究出什麼來了
What did you get with the tunnel searches?

899
01:05:41,020 --> 01:05:44,270
提醒我得把這愣頭青給踢走
Remind me to tell detail to keep hot heads out.

900
01:05:44,350 --> 01:05:46,510
我們在那下面有一隊人 那是一個龐大的網絡
We had teams down there. It's a huge network.

901
01:05:46,510 --> 01:05:47,970
那再多派些人
Well get more then.

902
01:05:48,050 --> 01:05:50,000
就走這條線索 我要找到他
Work the grid. I want him found.

903
01:05:50,090 --> 01:05:52,450
是的 那個面具男 我們這就去
Yeah, the masked man. We're on it.

904
01:05:52,540 --> 01:05:55,370
把制服脫了 你現在跟我了
Lose the uniform. You』re working for me now.

905
01:05:55,490 --> 01:05:57,910
我們現在可是需要些愣頭青
We could some hot head around here.

906
01:05:58,060 --> 01:05:59,770
長官 Daggett的死因不會只是個巧合
Sir, Daggett's death could only be a coincidence.

907
01:05:59,880 --> 01:06:01,650
你現在是個警探了孩子
You're a detective now, son.

908
01:06:01,800 --> 01:06:05,610
已經不能再相信巧合這種事情的存在了
You're not allowed to believe in coincidences anymore.

909
01:06:16,780 --> 01:06:19,910
- 沒人應門 - 沒有
- Nobody's answering. - No ...

910
01:06:20,010 --> 01:06:24,230
- 現在就我一個人了 - 你有鑰匙麼
- I'm on my own now. - Do you have keys?

911
01:06:25,090 --> 01:06:26,700
我從來沒使用過
I never needed them.

912
01:06:33,000 --> 01:06:35,270
我希望你不介意用我的錢
I hope you didn't liked reaching my money.

913
01:06:35,310 --> 01:06:37,610
要遭這樣的罪
Suffering this character.

914
01:06:44,110 --> 01:06:47,300
Bruce 我會好好照管你父母的心血
I'll take care of your parents legacy, Bruce.

915
01:06:48,800 --> 01:06:50,900
是誰
Who's this?

916
01:06:57,800 --> 01:06:59,690
Alfred去哪兒了
Where is Alfred?

917
01:07:00,990 --> 01:07:02,890
他走了
He left.

918
01:07:04,200 --> 01:07:06,100
還把所有東西都
...taking everything...

919
01:07:30,000 --> 01:07:35,000
- 那是什麼 - 我們剛剛好像斷電了
- What's that? - Our power has been shut off.

920
01:07:40,100 --> 01:07:42,190
你很會生火啊
You're good at that.

921
01:07:42,500 --> 01:07:45,300
我小時候 家裡一貧如洗
When I was a child, we had almost nothing.

922
01:07:45,400 --> 01:07:51,200
可每當夜晚我們生起火 就會覺得好像無比富有
But on the nights when we had a fire, We felt very rich indeed...

923
01:07:52,200 --> 01:07:55,610
我原以為你家境殷實
I assumed your family was wealthy.

924
01:07:56,010 --> 01:08:00,110
我小時候那會兒還沒有
Not always not when I was young.

925
01:08:00,710 --> 01:08:05,390
- 那是個老錯了 - 我自己也犯過
- It's an old mistake. - I had a few myself.

926
01:08:06,700 --> 01:08:09,100
還不止一兩個
More than a few.

927
01:08:10,700 --> 01:08:14,290
我們可以今晚就走
I could leave tonight.

928
01:08:14,490 --> 01:08:19,100
坐我的飛機去我們想去的地方
Take my plane and go anywhere we wanted.

929
01:08:20,310 --> 01:08:24,600
也許等將來哪天吧 今晚不行
Some day perhaps. Not tonight.

930
01:08:52,900 --> 01:08:55,000
別害羞啊
Don't be shy!

931
01:08:56,800 --> 01:08:59,210
Wayne說你可以把"清洗程序"給我
Wayne said that you can get me the 'Clean Slate'.

932
01:08:59,410 --> 01:09:02,510
- 那要看 - 看什麼
- That depends ... - On what?

933
01:09:02,610 --> 01:09:04,200
看你想用它做什麼事
On what you want it for..

934
01:09:04,300 --> 01:09:07,400
我要確保它不會落入錯誤之手
I have acquire it to keep it out of the wrong hands.

935
01:09:07,500 --> 01:09:10,000
還是不信任我是吧
Still don't trust me huh...

936
01:09:10,200 --> 01:09:15,120
- 我們要怎麼改變這點呢 - 就從帶我去見Bane開始
- How can we change that? - Start by taking me to Bane.

937
01:09:18,060 --> 01:09:19,840
是你要求的
You asked...

938
01:09:21,720 --> 01:09:24,190
從這裡開始 Bane的人會巡查隧道
From here, Bane's man patrol the tunnels

939
01:09:24,190 --> 01:09:26,480
而他們可不是你平時打架消遣的對象
and they're not your average brawlers.

940
01:09:27,120 --> 01:09:28,760
我也不是
Neither am I.

941
01:09:36,350 --> 01:09:37,400
- 他在你後面 - 誰
- He's behind you! - Who?

942
01:09:37,470 --> 01:09:38,960
我
Me!

943
01:09:43,910 --> 01:09:45,290
你以為自己在往哪兒走
Where do you think you're going? ...

944
01:09:58,090 --> 01:09:59,850
別這麼霸氣
Less a little bully.

945
01:10:07,340 --> 01:10:10,090
我總要想辦法不讓他們殺了我吧
I had to find a way to stop them trying to kill me.

946
01:10:10,200 --> 01:10:12,900
你犯了一個嚴重的錯誤
You made a serious mistake.

947
01:10:12,990 --> 01:10:16,120
恐怕沒有你犯的
Not as serious as yours ...

948
01:10:16,190 --> 01:10:18,350
要嚴重
... I fear.

949
01:10:21,300 --> 01:10:26,400
- Bane - 我們可別就這麼站著啊
- Bane ... - Let's not stand on so moody here.

950
01:10:27,100 --> 01:10:30,080
Wayne先生
Mr. Wayne ...

951
01:10:40,800 --> 01:10:42,700
平靜削弱你
Peace has cost you your strength.

952
01:10:42,800 --> 01:10:45,280
勝利擊垮你
Victory has defeated you.

953
01:11:46,870 --> 01:11:49,630
這些謊言欺詐
The adaptability and deception ...

954
01:11:49,740 --> 01:11:52,470
只能蒙蔽那些無知的人
powerful agents ... to the uninitiated people.

955
01:11:52,560 --> 01:11:56,210
只有我們心知肚明 不是麼 Bruce
But we are initiated aren't we, Bruce?

956
01:11:56,300 --> 01:11:58,970
我們都是影武者聯盟的一員
Members of the League of Shadows.

957
01:12:01,140 --> 01:12:03,540
可你背叛了我們
And you betrayed us.

958
01:12:04,520 --> 01:12:10,270
是啊 你被一群精神變態們給驅逐了
Yes. You were excommunicated by a gang of psychopaths.

959
01:12:14,000 --> 01:12:17,310
我 就是影武者
I am the League of Shadows.

960
01:12:17,400 --> 01:12:21,340
我來到這裡是為了完成忍者大師的遺志
I'm here to fulfill Ra's Al Ghul's destiny!

961
01:12:34,250 --> 01:12:38,470
你打起來倒像是個年輕人 完全不留後路
You fight like a younger man, there's nothing held back.

962
01:12:38,820 --> 01:12:42,890
很可敬 不過也是個錯誤
It's admirable, but mistaken.

963
01:12:46,480 --> 01:12:50,120
你以為黑暗是站在你一邊的嗎
You think darkness is your ally?

964
01:12:50,210 --> 01:12:56,030
你僅僅只是適應了黑暗 而我是因黑暗而生
You've merely adopted the dark, I was born in it.

965
01:12:56,160 --> 01:12:59,360
由黑暗而鑄
Molded by it ...

966
01:12:59,550 --> 01:13:02,930
直到成年以後 我才得見天日
I didn't see the light until I was already a man.

967
01:13:03,060 --> 01:13:06,090
但我只覺得光明很刺眼
By then was nothing to be blinded.

968
01:13:08,650 --> 01:13:13,150
暗影背棄了你 是因為他們屬於我
Shadows betray you because they belong to me!

969
01:13:17,940 --> 01:13:21,540
讓我來告訴你我是以何處為家的吧
I'll show you where I had made my home.

970
01:13:21,640 --> 01:13:25,240
在準備著審判之時
Whilst preparing to bring justice.

971
01:13:27,180 --> 01:13:29,880
我會擊潰你
Then I will break you.

972
01:13:38,130 --> 01:13:42,350
你那珍貴的軍庫 我就不客氣的收下了
Your precious armory! Great fully accepted.

973
01:13:42,450 --> 01:13:44,750
我們會需要用到的
We'll need it.

974
01:13:53,020 --> 01:13:57,020
啊是的 我一直在好奇是哪一樣東西會更先崩潰
Ah yes! I was wondering what would weight first...

975
01:14:01,210 --> 01:14:03,300
是你的精神
Your spirit ...

976
01:14:07,370 --> 01:14:09,480
還是你的肉體
... or your body?

977
01:14:53,180 --> 01:14:54,390
請給我接Gordon局長
Get me Commissioner Gordon.

978
01:14:54,480 --> 01:14:56,490
關於議員被綁一案我有了一條線索
I got a line up of Congressman's kidnapping.

979
01:15:09,180 --> 01:15:10,580
- 不好意思 小姐 - 什麼
- Excuse me, miss! - Yes?

980
01:15:10,680 --> 01:15:13,890
我需要檢查您的機票和證件
I'm going to need to see your ticket and identification, please.

981
01:15:14,190 --> 01:15:16,690
不介意幫我拿下嗎
Do you mind?

982
01:15:28,790 --> 01:15:31,690
我把你的照片給議員看了 猜猜怎麼著
I showed your picture to The Congressman. Guess what?!

983
01:15:32,090 --> 01:15:36,090
- 不要告訴我 他還想著我 - 神魂顛倒
- Don't tell me. Still in love? - Oh head over heels.

984
01:15:36,290 --> 01:15:37,990
不過還是準備起訴你
Pressing charges though.

985
01:15:38,190 --> 01:15:41,880
你犯了些錯啊 Kyle小姐
You've made some mistakes, Miss Kyle.

986
01:15:42,080 --> 01:15:45,880
- 姑娘家也要討生活嘛 - 喲你胃口可真好
- Girl's got to eat. - And you have an appetite.

987
01:15:45,980 --> 01:15:48,280
為什麼要逃 你這樣的犯罪記錄是逃不掉的
Why would run? You can't hide from us with a record like this.

988
01:15:48,380 --> 01:15:52,600
- 也許我不是在躲你呢 - 那你在躲誰 Bane嘛
- Maybe it's not you I'm running from. - Who then? Bane?

989
01:15:52,700 --> 01:15:54,290
你對他瞭解多少
What do you know about him?

990
01:15:54,390 --> 01:15:58,280
我只知道你應該像我一樣害怕他
About you should be as afraid of him as I am.

991
01:15:58,380 --> 01:16:00,480
我們可以給你提供保護
We can offer you protection.

992
01:16:03,390 --> 01:16:05,090
好吧
Okay ...

993
01:16:09,180 --> 01:16:10,820
我發現你的時候 其實
When I spotted you,

994
01:16:10,830 --> 01:16:13,580
我是在找我的一個朋友 Bruce Wayne
 I was looking for a friend of mine, Bruce Wayne.

995
01:16:15,620 --> 01:16:17,420
他死了嗎
Did that killed him?

996
01:16:18,920 --> 01:16:21,120
我不確定
I'm not sure.

