02:01:01,430 --> 02:01:03,940
- 有指數了 - 六點鐘方向有僱傭兵
- I got it! - Mercenaries at your 6.

1483
02:01:04,240 --> 02:01:07,780
別動 手舉在我們能看到的地方
Stand still! Keep your hands where we can see them!

1484
02:01:09,410 --> 02:01:12,160
Gordon局長 你被捕了
Commissioner Gordon, you're under arrest.

1485
02:01:12,160 --> 02:01:13,470
誰給你的權利
On who's authority?

1486
02:01:13,470 --> 02:01:15,670
哥譚人民
People of Gotham.

1487
02:01:15,670 --> 02:01:20,770
沒律師 沒證人 這算什麼聽證會
No lawyer. No witnesses. What sort of due process is this?

1488
02:01:20,770 --> 02:01:22,490
你已經被認定有罪了
You guilt have been determined.

1489
02:01:22,490 --> 02:01:24,480
這不過是量刑聽證會
This is merely a sentencing hearing.

1490
02:01:24,480 --> 02:01:26,920
你選什麼
Now what will it be?

1491
02:01:26,920 --> 02:01:29,880
死刑還是流放
Death or exile?

1492
02:01:29,980 --> 02:01:35,070
Crane 你以為我們會自願走上冰層麼
Crane, if you think we're going out on that ice willingly,

1493
02:01:35,070 --> 02:01:37,750
你錯了
you have another thing coming.

1494
02:01:39,030 --> 02:01:41,900
- 那就是死刑咯 - 我想是的
- Death then. - Looks that way.

1495
02:01:41,900 --> 02:01:45,340
很好 死刑
Very well. Death!

1496
02:01:45,940 --> 02:01:48,400
以流放的形式
By exile.

1497
02:01:50,130 --> 02:01:52,600
帶她來見我
Bring her to me!

1498
02:01:58,420 --> 02:02:00,730
嘿 下來 準備好
Hey. Going down. Get things ready.

1499
02:02:00,750 --> 02:02:02,750
行動開始
Let's gear on.

1500
02:02:09,930 --> 02:02:11,930
抓到了這傢伙 明天有得忙了
Spot this one on the spot. Got a big day tomorrow.

1501
02:02:12,030 --> 02:02:14,830
就是啊 不是每天都能逮到Bruce Wayne的
We all do. Not every day you bag Bruce Wayne!

1502
02:02:17,530 --> 02:02:19,140
- Bruce - 你沒事吧
- Bruce? - You okay?

1503
02:02:19,140 --> 02:02:21,540
你太會挑時間旅行了 Wayne先生
You pick the hell of time to go on vacation, Mr. Wayne.

1504
02:02:21,540 --> 02:02:23,340
我們還有多少時間
How long until that core ignites?

1505
02:02:23,340 --> 02:02:25,220
那核彈還有12個小時就炸了
That bomb goes off in 12 hours.

1506
02:02:25,220 --> 02:02:27,890
除非我們把它弄回反應堆裡
Unless we can reconnect it to the reactor.

1507
02:02:27,890 --> 02:02:31,660
- 你能把Miranda帶出去嗎 - 今晚不行 抱歉了
- Can you get Miranda out of here? - Not tonight. I'm sorry.

1508
02:02:31,660 --> 02:02:34,490
- 做你要做的 - 今晚我需要你
- Do what necessary. - Tonight I need you.

1509
02:02:34,500 --> 02:02:36,770
- 做什麼 - 讓我重回戰場
- What for? - To get me back in the game.

1510
02:02:36,770 --> 02:02:38,410
不好意思 掃你們的興了
Sorry to spoil things

1511
02:02:38,410 --> 02:02:41,830
孩子們 他們想親自處理這幾個人
boys but they want these guys to themselves.

1512
02:02:43,300 --> 02:02:46,460
- 我不會忘記我們事的 Miranda - 我知道
- I won't forget about us, Miranda! - I know.

1513
02:02:55,410 --> 02:02:59,020
- 我喜歡你的女朋友 Wayne先生 - 女朋友個頭
- I like your girlfriend, Mr. Wayne! - He should be so lucky.

1514
02:03:05,300 --> 02:03:07,880
我動一下Bane或是那炸彈
Any move I make on Bane or the bomb,

1515
02:03:07,880 --> 02:03:10,170
觸發者都會引爆炸彈
the trigger-man will set it off.

1516
02:03:10,170 --> 02:03:13,220
他們不會用無線電或是手機信號 太多干擾了
They won』t use radio or cell, too much interference.

1517
02:03:13,220 --> 02:03:15,030
紅外線的範圍沒那麼廣
Infrared doesn't have the range.

1518
02:03:15,030 --> 02:03:17,920
一定是某種長射程的微型脈衝
It had to be a Micro-burst, long-range.

1519
02:03:17,920 --> 02:03:19,740
- 你能攔截嗎 - 能
- Can you block it? - Yes.

1520
02:03:19,740 --> 02:03:23,920
但我需要蝙蝠車上的頻率捕獲器
But I need the EMP cannon guidance mounted on the Bat.

1521
02:03:23,920 --> 02:03:26,450
記得你停在哪兒了嘛
Remember where you parked it?

1522
02:03:40,460 --> 02:03:43,900
- 飛起來還好吧 - 好啊
- It fly okay? - Yeah.

1523
02:03:44,330 --> 02:03:46,840
雖然不能自動駕駛 真是謝謝了
Even without the autopilot. Thanks.

1524
02:03:46,840 --> 02:03:49,550
自動駕駛 你自己不能開啊
Autopilot? That's what you're there for.

1525
02:04:28,770 --> 02:04:31,410
安全了 來吧 快 過來
Thing's clear. Come on, quick! Climb.

1526
02:04:41,560 --> 02:04:43,080
封鎖起來
Lock it up!

1527
02:04:47,500 --> 02:04:49,280
你是誰
Who are you?

1528
02:05:18,090 --> 02:05:20,140
點燃它
Light it up!

1529
02:05:37,250 --> 02:05:39,250
媽媽 你看
Mom check it out.

1530
02:05:39,520 --> 02:05:41,390
親愛的 快看
Honey, take a look!

1531
02:05:50,520 --> 02:05:52,790
不可思議
Impossible!

1532
02:05:53,630 --> 02:05:57,810
看緊她 他會回來救她的
Keep her close! He'll come for her.

1533
02:05:57,810 --> 02:06:01,890
- Miranda Tate在哪兒 - Bane帶走了她
- Where's Miranda Tate? - Bane took her.

1534
02:06:01,890 --> 02:06:05,370
他佔領了市議會 守衛森嚴
He holds up city hall, surrounded by his army.

1535
02:06:05,370 --> 02:06:07,840
這個會截斷引爆信號
This blocks detonator signal to the bomb.

1536
02:06:07,840 --> 02:06:10,310
在日出前裝好
Get it on to it before sunrise.

1537
02:06:10,310 --> 02:06:12,690
必要的話 我會在開始時引爆核彈的
If I hit the button when it starts.

1538
02:06:12,690 --> 02:06:15,560
- 什麼開始時 - 戰爭
- When what start? - War.

1539
02:06:51,670 --> 02:06:52,830
還有一個沒倒呢
You missed a spot.

1540
02:06:55,970 --> 02:06:59,140
如果你獨自一人行俠仗義 戴個面具
If you're working alone, wear a mask!

1541
02:06:59,140 --> 02:07:01,460
我不畏懼直面他們
I'm not afraid if they see me standing up to these guys.

1542
02:07:01,460 --> 02:07:02,840
面具不為保護自己
The mask is not for you,

1543
02:07:02,840 --> 02:07:05,260
是為了保護你在意的人
it's to protect the people you care about.

1544
02:07:06,090 --> 02:07:08,950
數到五丟出去
Count to five and throw.

1545
02:07:18,900 --> 02:07:21,800
嘿 無意冒犯 但你就沒有火力大點的東西嗎
Hey no offense, but you got something bigger in that belt?

1546
02:07:31,600 --> 02:07:34,520
- 現在怎麼辦 - 全力攻擊Bane
- What now? - All out assault on Bane.

1547
02:07:34,520 --> 02:07:37,340
但你得帶人們過橋
But you need to get people across the bridge.

1548
02:07:37,340 --> 02:07:38,040
為什麼
Why?

1549
02:07:38,040 --> 02:07:42,680
以免我們失敗了 離開哥譚 能救多少救多少
In case we fail. Leave an exodus. Save as many lives as you can.

1550
02:07:42,680 --> 02:07:47,230
- 你不需要我嗎 - 你已經給了我一支軍隊 現在 快走
- You don't need me here? - You given me an army. Now, go!

1551
02:07:47,530 --> 02:07:50,370
- 好吧 謝謝 - 先別謝我
- Alright, thanks! - Don't thank me yet.

1552
02:07:50,370 --> 02:07:53,660
我怕以後就沒機會了
Well I might not get the chance later.

1553
02:08:06,280 --> 02:08:07,740
你真是太客氣了
You shouldn't have.

1554
02:08:08,950 --> 02:08:11,380
隧道被殘骸堵住了
All in town tunnel blocked by debris.

1555
02:08:11,380 --> 02:08:14,700
但加農炮的火力足夠為人們開道
But the cannon have anough fire power to make a path for people.

1556
02:08:14,710 --> 02:08:16,490
等到戰鬥開始前
Wait until the fighting begins!

1557
02:08:16,490 --> 02:08:19,780
你要為了你女友升級這場戰爭嗎
You going to wage your war to save your stuck up girlfriend?

1558
02:08:19,790 --> 02:08:22,140
要發動 閥門
To start it, throttle.

1559
02:08:22,140 --> 02:08:23,370
我會開
I got it.

1560
02:08:23,370 --> 02:08:25,790
你有45分鐘拯救哥譚
We have 45 minutes to save the city.

1561
02:08:25,790 --> 02:08:29,390
不 我有45分鐘逃離炸彈輻射區
No. I got 45 minutes to get clear of the blast radius.

1562
02:08:29,420 --> 02:08:30,790
因為你毫無勝算
because you don't stand a chance against these guys.

1563
02:08:30,790 --> 02:08:32,250
有你幫助 也許還有希望
With your help, I might.

1564
02:08:32,250 --> 02:08:35,160
我會打開隧道 然後離開
I open that tunnel, but then I'm gone.

1565
02:08:35,160 --> 02:08:38,710
你心裡有更好的一面
There's more to you than that.

1566
02:08:40,850 --> 02:08:44,140
不好意思一直讓你失望
Sorry to keep letting you down.

1567
02:08:46,560 --> 02:08:51,820
跟我走吧 救救你自己
Come with me! Save yourself!

1568
02:08:53,210 --> 02:08:58,450
你不欠那些人什麼 你已經為他們付出了一切
You don't owe these people anymore. You given them everything.

1569
02:08:58,450 --> 02:09:02,290
不是一切 還沒有
Not everything. Not yet.

1570
02:09:41,830 --> 02:09:46,290
散開 散開不然格殺勿論
Disperse! Disperse or be fired upon!

1571
02:09:47,120 --> 02:09:50,060
這座城裡只有一個警察局
There's only one police in this town,

1572
02:10:28,390 --> 02:10:30,420
開火
Open fire!

1573
02:11:21,420 --> 02:11:23,490
- 來了 - 準備好
- Here it comes. - Get ready!

1574
02:11:52,860 --> 02:11:57,450
所以你回來給你的城市陪葬麼
So you came back to die with your city!

1575
02:11:57,450 --> 02:12:01,470
不 我回來阻止你
No. I came back to stop you.

1576
02:12:12,490 --> 02:12:13,600
現在
Now!

1577
02:12:26,540 --> 02:12:27,620
這不可能
That's impossible.

1578
02:12:29,460 --> 02:12:31,420
去第五大道!
Come over the fifth!

1579
02:12:46,070 --> 02:12:50,020
上車 去 你過來 你也是
Get on the bus, go ahead. You come with me! You too!

1580
02:12:50,020 --> 02:12:53,410
嘿 你 你和你 過來
Hey you, you and you, come here!

1581
02:12:53,410 --> 02:12:55,350
其他人上車 好麼
Everyone else get on the bus! Okay.

1582
02:12:55,350 --> 02:12:56,370
你們 挨家挨戶的敲門
You guys, you're going

1583
02:12:56,370 --> 02:12:58,370
把消息傳開 就說
to knock on doors and spread the word okay.

1584
02:12:58,370 --> 02:13:01,510
炸彈快爆炸了 從南街隧道離開
The bomb going to go off. Get out by South Street tunnel.

1585
02:13:01,540 --> 02:13:02,630
或者穿過橋
or over the bridge.

1586
02:13:02,640 --> 02:13:04,280
每個人兩個街區
You go, you do two blocks,

1587
02:13:04,280 --> 02:13:06,880
傳完話就回車上來 好嗎 去吧
you get back to the bus. Alright? Go! Go!

1588
02:13:07,680 --> 02:13:11,860
- 他回來了嗎 - 等著看吧 快走
- Is he back? - Keep your eyes open. Go!

1589
02:14:33,900 --> 02:14:36,090
去守門
Cover the doors!

1590
02:14:38,820 --> 02:14:41,950
引爆器在哪兒 在哪兒
Where's your trigger? Where is it?

1591
02:14:43,060 --> 02:14:46,440
你不會給普通市民的
You never gave it to any ordinary citizen.

1592
02:14:46,440 --> 02:14:49,050
在哪兒 引爆器在哪兒
Where is it? Where's the trigger?

1593
02:14:49,360 --> 02:14:52,130
在哪兒
Where is it?

1594
02:15:00,380 --> 02:15:03,880
告訴我引爆器在哪兒
Tell me where the trigger is.

1595
02:15:03,880 --> 02:15:06,740
然後 我准許你死
Then, you have my permission to die.

1596
02:15:18,700 --> 02:15:23,790
我把你廢了 你怎麼回來的
I broke you. How did you come back?

1597
02:15:23,800 --> 02:15:25,400
你以為你是唯一一個
You think you're the only

1598
02:15:25,400 --> 02:15:28,150
可以從那逃離的人嗎
one who could learn the strength to escape?

1599
02:15:28,150 --> 02:15:32,820
- 引爆器在哪兒 - 但我從未逃離過
- Where's the trigger? - But I never escaped.

1600
02:15:33,590 --> 02:15:35,990
但那孩子
But the child,

1601
02:15:36,890 --> 02:15:39,520
忍者大師的孩子 飛躍淵井的孩子
Child of Ra's Al Ghul's, who made the climb.

1602
02:15:39,520 --> 02:15:42,780
但他不是忍者大師的孩子
But he's not the child of Ra's Al Ghul.

1603
02:15:45,450 --> 02:15:47,360
我才是
I am.

1604
02:15:47,360 --> 02:15:53,170
儘管我並不普通 但我也是個市民
Although I'm not ordinary, I'm a citizen.

1605
02:16:12,350 --> 02:16:13,880
Miranda
Miranda?

1606
02:16:16,290 --> 02:16:17,650
為什麼
Why?

1607
02:16:17,950 --> 02:16:23,620
Talia 我媽媽臨死前 給我取名叫Talia
Talia. My mother named me Talia before she was killed.

1608
02:16:23,630 --> 02:16:29,570
如果不是Bane一直守護我 我也早就死了
The way I have been killed if not for my protector, Bane.

1609
02:16:37,250 --> 02:16:38,370
再見
Good bye.

1610
02:16:40,490 --> 02:16:43,480
我爬出了淵井
I climbed out of the pit.

1611
02:16:48,500 --> 02:16:51,050
找到了我的父親
I found my father

1612
02:16:53,180 --> 02:16:57,080
帶他回去血債血償
and brought him back to exact terrible vengeance.

1613
02:16:57,080 --> 02:16:59,130
但那時
But by that time,

1614
02:16:59,230 --> 02:17:04,230
獄徒們和醫生已經對我的朋友下了毒手
the prisoners and the doctor had their work to my friend,

1615
02:17:04,230 --> 02:17:05,520
我的守護者
my protector.

1616
02:17:09,290 --> 02:17:12,490
影武者聯盟接納了我們 訓練了我們
The League took us in and trained us

1617
02:17:12,490 --> 02:17:16,640
但我的父親無法接受Bane
but my father could not accept Bane.

1618
02:17:16,640 --> 02:17:20,280
他認為他是魔鬼 他的存在
He saw only a monster, whose very existence

1619
02:17:20,280 --> 02:17:24,450
象徵著他妻子被囚禁並死去的地獄
was the reminder of the hell he left his wife to die in.

1620
02:17:24,460 --> 02:17:27,840
他把Bane逐出了影武者聯盟
He excommunicated Bane from The League of Shadows.

1621
02:17:27,840 --> 02:17:33,150
他唯一的罪就是他愛上了我
His only crime was that he loved me.

1622
02:17:34,360 --> 02:17:38,060
我一直無法原諒我的父親
I could not forgive my father.

1623
02:17:41,710 --> 02:17:44,270
直到你殺了他
Until you murdered him.

1624
02:18:01,290 --> 02:18:06,750
他試圖殺死數以百萬的無辜之人
He was trying to kill millions of innocent people.

1625
02:18:06,790 --> 02:18:11,920
在哥譚 無辜這個詞未免言過其實
Innocence is a strong word to throw around Gotham roose.

1626
02:18:13,310 --> 02:18:17,060
我以完成他的大業向他致敬
I honor my father by finishing his work.

1627
02:18:28,410 --> 02:18:31,120
手刃殺父仇人
Vengeance against the man who killed

1628
02:18:31,120 --> 02:18:34,120
不過是對我耐心的獎勵
him is simply a reward for my patience.

1629
02:18:35,140 --> 02:18:36,420
你看
You see?

1630
02:18:37,370 --> 02:18:42,440
就是這種遲鈍的刀子 這種花時間的刀子
It's the slow knife. The knife that takes it's time.

1631
02:18:45,470 --> 02:18:51,100
那種隱忍多年 充滿執念的刀子 
The knife that wait years, without forgetting,

1632
02:18:51,110 --> 02:18:55,600
悄然滑入骨間
then slip quietly between the bones,

1633
02:18:55,600 --> 02:19:00,110
入肉最深
that's the knife that cut deepest.

1634
02:19:00,180 --> 02:19:01,930
求求你
Please!

1635
02:19:08,800 --> 02:19:12,730
也許那刀子太鈍了
Maybe that knife was too slow.

1636
02:19:12,790 --> 02:19:14,830
卡車被襲擊了
The truck is under attacked.

1637
02:19:14,830 --> 02:19:18,270
Gordon 你給了他屏蔽我的信號的方法
Gordon. You gave him a way to block my signal

1638
02:19:18,570 --> 02:19:20,560
無所謂
No matter.

1639
02:19:22,360 --> 02:19:25,410
哥譚不過能多苟延殘喘11分鐘而已
He's bought Gotham 11 minutes.

1640
02:19:25,990 --> 02:19:27,990
快點
Come on!

1641
02:19:35,000 --> 02:19:37,020
退回去 你想幹嘛
Stay back! What are you doing?

1642
02:19:37,020 --> 02:19:40,590
Blake 重案組 我要送他們去安全的地方
Blake. MCU, I'm getting these boys to safety

1643
02:19:40,590 --> 02:19:42,550
你會害死我們的
You're going to get us all killed.

1644
02:19:42,550 --> 02:19:45,680
如果有人越過這座橋 他們就會炸了整座城
If anyone cross this bridge, they'll blow up the city.

1645
02:19:45,680 --> 02:19:48,880
反正都會爆炸的 我們需要打開這座橋 現在
It going to blow up anyway. We need to open this bridge, now!

1646
02:19:48,880 --> 02:19:52,650
警官 如果你向前一步 我們就開槍了
Detective, if you take one step forward we will shoot you!

1647
02:19:52,650 --> 02:19:56,420
如果再走一步 我們就會炸橋
If you do two forward, we will blow the bridge.

1648
02:19:58,410 --> 02:20:00,740
回車上等我
Go back to the bus and wait for me alright!

1649
02:20:00,740 --> 02:20:01,940
回去等著就好
